actionConfiguration.body:
Update model_master
set
model_name = {{model_name.text}},
version = {{version.text}},
model_type = {{model_type.selectedOptionValue}},
framework = {{framework.selectedOptionValue}},
framework_version = {{framework_version.text}},
base_algorithm = {{base_algorithm.selectedOptionValue}},
file_location = {{file_location.selectedOptionValue}},
primary_file_loc = {{primary_file_location.text}},
primary_file_name = {{primary_file_name.text}},
secondary_file_loc = {{secondary_file_location.text}},
secondary_file_name = {{secondary_file_name.text}},
description = {{description.text}},
min_gpu_ram = {{minimum_gpu_ram.text}},
number_of_cuda ={{cuda.text}},
edited_by = {{edited_by.text}},
edited_date = current_timestamp()
where model_id = {{Table1.selectedRow.model_id}};
